# Brewfile.mbp — overlay specific to the "mbp" machine (work)
# Loaded IN ADDITION to the global Brewfile by the brew role when host == mbp.
# Populate when the mbp/mini distinction is finalized (open question in host_vars).
#
# Example:
# cask "datagrip"      # if reserved for work machine
# brew "awscli"        # if reserved for work machine
